extendedInfo.description: Welcome to the Official Android App for Keller Graduate School of Management.***The 2.5 Update is Here Download it Today!***--------------Signing Into the app---------------The Home sign in screen requires you to use your Student Portal login user name and password from my.devry.edu.The Go To Class sign in requires you to use your eCollege login user name and password from devryu.net.---------------------------------------------------------Keller Mobile is the new mobile connection to Keller Graduate School of Management and the Keller Graduate School of Management eLearning platform.Highlights Include:Posting to Threaded DiscussionsReviewing your scheduleChecking your gradesAsk Keller Resetting your portal and eLearning passwords---------------------------------------------------------We look forward to the continued progress and improvement of this App for your student experience.  Your feedback is needed and it is greatly appreciated, keep it coming!Sincerely,DeVry IT Mobile Support

reviews.title: Perfection
reviews.comment: As long as you know you\'re log in creds this works perfectly. Like the option that keeps you logged in so you only have to enter it once. SSO to ecollege eventually would be a nice feature & it could cut down on log in confusion for some.
reviews.author: Cathy Vroom

reviews.title: Crashes

reviews.title: Still new
reviews.comment: The first roll out worked fine. The app then updated and now it doesn\'t open. It just doesn\'t open now.
